comments: Williamson (NOP) trails Curry (GSW) during his driving shot attempt and the marginal contact is created by Curry extending his legs and arm behind him.
Thompson (GSW) clenaly dislodges the ball from Williamson (NOP) after his gather.
Williamson (NOP) initiates contact with Wiggins' (GSW) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
McCollum (NOP) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before releasing his jump shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) legally contests McCollum's (NOP) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Williamson (NOP) establishes himself in Wiggins' (GSW) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Green (GSW) is not established in a legal guarding position in Williamson's (NOP) path when body contact occurs that affects his SQBR.
Daniels (NOP) establishes himself in Wiggins' (GSW) path and does not deliver illegal contact during the elevator screen.
Jones (NOP) establishes himself in Wiggins' (GSW) path and does not deliver illegal contact during the elevator screen.
Curry (GSW) reaches in and initiates some contact with Williamson's (NOP) wrist, which he moves through and maintains possession.
Green (GSW) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Jones' (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Murphy III (NOP) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.

Replay review of the foul called on Wiggins (GSW) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Wiggins grabs Murphy III's (NOP) arm and initiates illegal contact before making contact with the ball.
Murphy III (NOP) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
